												<ECUC-STRING-PARAM-DEF UUID="c2685740-2596-46e5-b367-77f803f9c19e">
													<SHORT-NAME>vSetAdditionalInitCode</SHORT-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">Specify additional code which can be referenced from the initialization callouts of EcuM and BswM.

E.g.: Mcu_InitClock()

If it is necessary to call a function with a module pointer from the global postbuild-loadable configuration, the placeholder %CONFIGPTR% can be used:

E.g.: Mcu_Init(%CONFIGPTR%)</L-2>
													</DESC>
